snippet.title: Backyard Baseball 2001 (PC) - Gameplay
snippet.description: A full (6-inning) game of Backyard Baseball 2001, a baseball computer game by Humongous Entertainment. Enjoy watching me forget to throw the ball back to the pitcher over and over.
